  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's words</h2><br>This is a game I developed independently from design to program maintenance,<br>First of all, I want to thank all the players who participated in the production,<br>It's your feedback that allows the game to be constantly revised and optimized, and has grown up to this day.<br>If you like sandbox observation, base construction, city defense games,<br>Find a quiet night and buy it for easy play,<br>I believe you can find some fun in it.<br>(っ´ω`c)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple kingdom simulation game</h2><br>The world of MiniMap Kingdom is a simple infinite sandbox,<br>You can freely change the terrain and build your own villages and towns on it,<br>Different villagers will be responsible for producing resources and defending cities,<br>The enemies will also build their own villages on the map,<br>Over time, the map will gradually expand and grow with the development of players and enemies,<br>The player can also be an observer watching the villagers live in the kingdom you build,<br>Hope you can enjoy this game.<br>(っ´ω`c)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Long-term development</h2><br>The basic structure of the minimap kingdom has been established,<br>I hope to add more units and content in the future,<br>And continue to optimize the effectiveness of the game to accommodate more units,<br>Reduce the problem of late game jams,<br>I will also spend time rewriting the game’s architecture when necessary,<br>Players’ gaming experience will be very helpful for development,<br>I will gradually adjust the direction of development with these feedbacks,<br>Hope that eventually the minimap kingdom can be turned into a simple, fun and long-lasting game,<br>Thank you for your participation!<br>(っ´ω`c)",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's words</h2><br>This is a game I developed independently from design to program maintenance,<br>First of all, I want to thank all the players who participated in the production,<br>It's your feedback that allows the game to be constantly revised and optimized, and has grown up to this day.<br>If you like sandbox observation, base construction, city defense games,<br>Find a quiet night and buy it for easy play,<br>I believe you can find some fun in it.<br>(っ´ω`c)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple kingdom simulation game</h2><br>The world of MiniMap Kingdom is a simple infinite sandbox,<br>You can freely change the terrain and build your own villages and towns on it,<br>Different villagers will be responsible for producing resources and defending cities,<br>The enemies will also build their own villages on the map,<br>Over time, the map will gradually expand and grow with the development of players and enemies,<br>The player can also be an observer watching the villagers live in the kingdom you build,<br>Hope you can enjoy this game.<br>(っ´ω`c)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Long-term development</h2><br>The basic structure of the minimap kingdom has been established,<br>I hope to add more units and content in the future,<br>And continue to optimize the effectiveness of the game to accommodate more units,<br>Reduce the problem of late game jams,<br>I will also spend time rewriting the game’s architecture when necessary,<br>Players’ gaming experience will be very helpful for development,<br>I will gradually adjust the direction of development with these feedbacks,<br>Hope that eventually the minimap kingdom can be turned into a simple, fun and long-lasting game,<br>Thank you for your participation!<br>(っ´ω`c)",
